MARKETING & SEO

Learn more

Server-side rendering

SSR infrastructure ensures crawlers can fully read site content. 

Structured data markup

Markup is automatically added to many page types with the option to edit or create your own at page and folder level. 

Sitemaps

We automatically create and submit an optimized sitemap, including image sitemaps, to Google Search Console.

Auto-generated robots.txt files

Retain full control and customize robots.txt files to tell bots which URLs to crawl.

INFRASTRUCTURE

Learn more

Multi-cloud hosting

With 99.98% uptime, agency and client sites stay up, even in regional outages, thanks to the unified power of AWS, Google Cloud, Fastly and our own data centers.

Limitless scalability

Every site has automatic scalability at its core, meaning businesses can go as big as they want. With over 4.5 billion daily requests, we can more than handle it.

Automatic disaster recovery

Automated systems and engineers constantly monitor sites, rerouting traffic to stable locations if unusual activity is identified, meaning any potential downtime is avoided.

Worldwide CDN coverage

Multiple data centers around the world—backed by 200, globally-distributed CDN nodes—guarantee best-in-class performance.
